snippet.textDisplay:
I'm so sorry that I have been away for so long and not to date.

This video got my attention tho, and shook me. The channel always made me happy and a bit at peace. I was in a hard place as i have to get my life straight and started. But all that can't be the excuse, as i have a lot of spare time and can always stay on date.

I liked this channel ever since i started watching it in 2014. When i was bored and scared of becoming older. Now I'm 19 still in the same house and with a weird life style. Especially now since its also lockdown here where i am.

So i will like to say that im coming back and gonna be back for a long time.

Also my favorite colony was and is still the Fire Ants. I was sad and shook when the first pasted away and made me kind of... sad. But still... they get my vote.

Be safe. Antscannada, and I'm looking forward for the next video.

Ant-Love forever
